<!--
  Wing Font sitemap.

  Hand-maintained — kept in sync with:
    * web/src/App.tsx               (main routes)
    * web/src/utils/const.ts        (AVAILABLE_FONTS → /specimen/:family)
    * .github/workflows/deploy-pages.yml

  When a new top-level route is added, append a <url> entry here.
  When a new font lands in AVAILABLE_FONTS, append a /specimen/<name>
  entry. The specimen list is restricted to fonts that are actually
  surfaced in the showcase / specimen page — hero subset fonts
  (Xiaolai-Huninn-hero-*) and dialect variants not present in
  AVAILABLE_FONTS aren't visitable, so they're excluded.

  `lastmod` reflects the date the sitemap itself was last edited
  rather than per-URL freshness, which keeps maintenance simple
  at the scale of this site (35 URLs total).

  priority is a soft signal to crawlers:
    1.0 — homepage
    0.9 — primary product pages (/showcase, /generate)
    0.7 — secondary informational pages (/about, /credits)
    0.4 — per-font specimen detail pages
    0.3 — legal pages

  Reference: https://www.sitemaps.org/protocol.html
-->
